cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS

The paper discusses the issues and challenges in providing secure communication and access control for mobile web service provisioning, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also addresses the challenges in providing reliable communication in volatile mobile ad-hoc topologies, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes a distributed semantics-based authorization mechanism, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed systems (cs.DS).
